{"tid":906162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非洲豬瘟】19省市淪陷！1日新增4疫情 上海首爆發 香港政府有冇防備？","createTime":"2018-11-17T17:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T03:26:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"373812e069d4e77742b8224547d5e0439fb3599a","tid":906162,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:32:03.000Z","msg":"（新增內容）內地農業農村部今日接連公佈多宗非洲豬瘟疫情，分別位於上海市金山區、江西省上饒市、雲南省昆明市及四川省成都市，當局稱已經處理受影響的豬隻，同時進行消毒，禁止生豬進入市場。<br />\n<br />\n內地農業農村部指出，經過中國動物衞生與流行病學中心確定，今日再有4地發生非洲豬溫疫情，其中上海是首次發現。當局稱已按照應急預案，進行封鎖、撲殺、無害化處理、消毒等程序，同時禁止所有生豬及其產品進出封鎖區。<br />\n<br />\n自內地今年8月初確診非洲豬瘟之後，至今日已有16省、3直轄市出現疫情，包括遼寧、吉林、黑龍江、內蒙古、山西、河南、天津、安徽、江蘇、浙江、湖南、貴州、雲南、重慶、湖北、江西、福建、四川及上海。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新華網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181117/58925649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58925649&d=Iy8f23t4%2Be1Fh2T7qfBAiDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9ede556b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58925649&h=5c816729\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181117/58925649</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋入咁撚名強國豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f0e6af87e37f01c0f1a3a29f09f9c4fb512ef8","tid":906162,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T20:37:09.000Z","msg":"有......L"},{"pid":"bfd11b4fbd840a1480c02d8a5e0958b40a58313b","tid":906162,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T22:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d197aa677ec2c114cb02750b7b98aed7275586","tid":906162,"uid":208722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,